<br>
Anyway, here are some of the things I'm gonna ask him about, please fill in what I've missed and perhaps a few of you would like to join up for a discussion in game.<br>
<br>
In game issues:<br>
* MA Specials Unique/No Drop annoyance.<br>
* General state of MA specials with skill lock times/damage and so on.<br>
* Book of Knowledge malfunction.<br>
* MA weapons; Damage output, bugs, 2handed MA weapons, punching with bow etc.<br>
* State of the &quot;Useless&quot; skills; Riposte, sharp objects etc.<br>
* Cohort and Horde nanos bugs.<br>
* Dimach damage output/timer.<br>
<br>
Short term upcoming changes:<br>
* &quot;Fist&quot; line of nanos getting changed in 14.0?<br>
* Kicks? Whats up with those exactly?<br>
<br>
Future enhancements to the MA profession:<br>
* New nanos? Enhance Personal Healing line? Enhance give life/energy line? <br>
* News on upcoming MA attacks? Any chance of more?<br>
<br>
And perhaps the biggest issue at the moment:<br>
* State of Phys Init. Is it really working as intended?<br>
<br>
<br>
Anyway, remember that this is an ARK, not a Funcom employee. He can probably not answer everything and though he has some insight into AO behind-the-scenes he isn't a game designer or a programmer. <br>
<br>
Anyway, bring on the stuff I've missed and if you wanna join in for the discussion. (I don't wanna crowd the ARK though.)<br>
